{"tid":1613983,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我老母親眼見到示威者收利是","createTime":"2019-10-02T16:19:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T16:43:34.000Z","uid":265123,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"69ae27b8c9d3387fc2da09570a065b3ac10a7c9e","tid":1613983,"uid":265123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:19:34.000Z","msg":"前排同老母嘈交佢一路話佢親眼見到班示威者收利是。然後又帶落外國勢力乜乜乜，標準藍絲無腦言論係到屌。當時我已經好好奇佢究竟睇到啲咩。今日佢收工係到同我老豆講，我終於知道<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我老母   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我老豆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:我今日又見到班人收利是啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:係啊，今日班人又出去搞事吖嘛<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:原來佢地收啲利是係暗號嚟㗎，唔同錢有唔同意思㗎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:封封利是得 $1.3, $1.4<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:唔夠錢派啦？得咁少<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:班人唔知開到咩利是又係到好興奮大叫，都唔知啲暗號係乜。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽到呢到我已經知我老母究竟睇到啲咩，真係好想帶佢地體驗下大學生活"},{"pid":"93b6534e67a046e121a910636d8b914f9d0bc541","tid":1613983,"uid":80200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:20:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bf3bb34fd89e4d0f42adcd3080959bdaa4b4e67","tid":1613983,"uid":192824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:23:13.000Z","msg":"我最後1.1"},{"pid":"6643e7ebf8d3fbb6a801402765b3258d9a3bb255","tid":1613983,"uid":138476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:30:52.000Z","msg":"標題黨唔好引人誤會啦<br />\n$1.3 = 個三 = GPA過三"},{"pid":"51a979cf242fa4fbbbb8b5aaabc10ca2181d7b3f","tid":1613983,"uid":43008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:31:34.000Z","msg":"係咪甲由改名1蚊3