6:34:41.000Z","msg":"劉卓天，學生，已失踪兩個月<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yY8h6ra.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyY8h6ra.jpg&h=c0534bca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96ab51879b447d0d0756769e743a98c354d0fd22","tid":1613983,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:35:32.000Z","msg":"有冇人解釋下"},{"pid":"123835f0240b0e83e341917d75bf3d30f7998a87","tid":1613983,"uid":5067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:38:12.000Z","msg":"我有10.4<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff97d8b0a670884b3b848e04ea11041a54a2ea02","tid":1613983,"uid":170987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:41:40.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，個三俾乞衣都唔夠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a4ef9695eaeffc30ea74e568f1cc4d276418681","tid":1613983,"uid":43657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"96ab51879b447d0d0756769e743a98c354d0fd22","tid":1613983,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:35:32.000Z","msg":"有冇人解釋下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:42:32.000Z","msg":"$1.3讀出黎係「過三」<br />\n通常組爸媽會開sem派利是俾組仔囡<br />\n一係俾「過三」一係「過四」<br />\n即係gpa會過三or爆四"},{"pid":"3f6cb8e85f0b4f7c3de674e9bc8c6e38520d812f","tid":1613983,"uid":127137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:43:34.000Z","msg":"開SEM利是<br />\n通常在開SEM後開SEM飯時由長輩(老鬼/組爸媽)派發，重意頭。<br />\n<br />\n$1.3 利是<br />\n開SEM利是的一種，取其諧音過三，即祝福接受利是的人GPA過三。<br />\n<br />\n$5.3利是<br />\n開SEM利是的一種，取其諧音唔過三，即詛咒接受利是的人GPA不過三。<br />\n1.2/1.4/5.2/10.2/10.3/10.4/100.3利是<br />\n<br />\n過三爆四<br />\n指GPA過三，成績優異，是莘莘學子共同的願望。由於中大GPA最高為4.0 ，所以中大學生只能「過三」，無法「爆四」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cuhkinfo.blogspot.com/2013/08/blog-post_14.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcuhkinfo.blogspot.com%2F2013%2F08%2Fblog-post_14.html%3Fm%3D1&d=Bbcm6JBZsUbsJrWfDZmHX2zUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=75c246df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cuhkinfo.blogspot.com/2013/08/blog-post_14.html?m=1</a>"}]}